      <pattern name="Custom page form replacement" location=".claude/skills/dataverse-deploy/SKILL.md">
        Form Component Control binds to a Custom Page web resource; replaces standard form display while form record is still the data store.
      </pattern>
    </patterns>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read task 035's audit note (`notes/research/035-form-customization-audit.md`). If recommendation is "escalate", PAUSE this task and flag in `current-task.md` for owner sign-off.</step>
    <step order="2">Confirm task 036 deployed `sprk_emailcomposer` web resource and smoke tests passed.</step>
    <step order="3">Choose mechanism: Form Component Control (preferred) vs primary form replacement. Document choice in task notes.</step>
    <step order="4">Create the new form binding in Dataverse:
      - **Option A (Form Component Control)**: add a custom control on a new Main form whose source is `sprk_emailcomposer` web resource; pass record context as URL params
      - **Option B (primary form replacement)**: create new Main form with embedded iframe/web resource control pointing to `sprk_emailcomposer?data=%7B%22mode%22%3A%22view%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22<recordId>%22%7D`
    </step>
    <step order="5">Set new form as primary (form order: new form first).</step>
    <step order="6">Set standard form to hidden / admin-only (assigned to admin security role only) — preserving NFR-07 reversibility. Task 039 documents the admin access path.</step>
    <step order="7">Publish customizations.</step>
    <step order="8">Manual smoke test:
      - Open an existing `sprk_communication` record from a view → confirm Code Page renders with view mode + correct record loaded
      - Edit / Reply / Forward actions in Code Page work
      - Switch to admin user role → confirm standard form accessible as fallback (per task 039's documented path)
    </step>
    <step order="9">Verify reversibility: temporarily restore standard form as primary (without code changes — purely form order toggle); confirm record still opens; restore swap.</step>
    <step order="10">Document deploy + smoke test in `projects/email-communication-solution-r3/notes/research/038-form-swap-deploy.md`.</step>
    <step order="11">Update `tasks/TASK-INDEX.md`: mark task 038 ✅ completed.</step>
    <step order="12">Update `current-task.md` per task-execute protocol: status → completed.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="dataverse-deploy">Form / customization deploy</tool>
    <tool name="dataverse-mcp-usage">Form metadata query if MCP available</tool>
    <tool name="write">Smoke-test note</tool>
  </tools>

